{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Upgrade </strong>your spells from basic functionality to a devastating power!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489560/extras/lightning_laser_-_Kopie.gif?t=1731783948\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Complete <strong>over 300 challenges</strong> to gain the advantage of <strong>over 300 interesting unlocks</strong>, with <strong>quite a lot</strong> of new additions to the game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489560/extras/unlocks_gif.gif?t=1731783948\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose from over <strong>30 different events</strong> which may trigger throughout a run for even more variety and build customizing!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489560/extras/prophecy_options.gif?t=1731783948\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play through <strong>multiple realms</strong>, each one providing a different type of playstyle to all of the character classes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Craft</strong> your own weapon to take with you and overcome the <strong>5 trials</strong> of each realm!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Will you become the archmage of Elewar or will you be brought down by your opponents? Bulletheaven might quickly become a bullethell if you aren't strong enouph!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every enemy has at least 1 special attack... which you can dodge! There is no simple contact damage, which makes the game <strong>very challenging</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>Feature list:</strong></u></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">5 elements, 20 different offensive spells and 8 utility spells.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every spell may be upgraded in its rarity separately, which enables a diverse and powerful spell progression in a run.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Prophecy Whirls, which give you a choice of a random event, may challenge and reward you depending on the chosen difficulty.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">18 character classes with wildly different playstyles, combined with a dual class system. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">over 300 unlocks with corresponding rewards. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Over 140 upgrades.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose an unlocked blessing before you start a run, making cool combinations out of classes, blessings and starting spells possible!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">At least 5 realms with different enemies, rules and trials.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Crafting system to make your own items, which give you an additional edge in the Trials of Elewar. There are 5 different equipment slots with varying crafting.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Several hidden secrets to discover.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A roguelike gamemode with a highly different gameplay.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And much much more!</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"First blood","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2489560/a8646a4bc6055c92a79ca6127212f9647f7cf608.jpg"},{"name":"Elite encounter #1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2489560/ea86783e0ce99e281ef69c685d7571ee5f62f640.jpg"},{"name":"Elite encounter #2","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2489560/e463ceb320d5a2124ddb7e022734a5f219dc05dd.jpg"},{"name":"The Beginning","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2489560/89c3519c80e96b31bb709c85868a29822fde8d8f.jpg"},{"name":"Magic Upgrade","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2489560/554539e458ab1ae85af432955a294ae6206da450.jpg"},{"name":"Rare Upgrade","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2489560/554539e458ab1ae85af432955a294ae6206da450.jpg"},{"name":"Legendary Upgrade","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2489560/554539e458ab1ae85af432955a294ae6206da450.jpg"},{"name":"Finalist","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2489560/f2d529ba2fa5b0079028bfbdd0afe419c54582ca.jpg"},{"name":"Break your limits","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2489560/a65f021eb228660ca7cbbf8d0322c80e54aa8f1d.jpg"},{"name":"Immortality?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2489560/af5361f073136e6e84e7e2e27f87067cc1340934.jpg"}],"total":45},"background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2489560?t=1731783948","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489560/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1731783948","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489560/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1731783948","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489560/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1731783948","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Steam Leaderboards","id":25}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Upgrade </strong>your spells from basic functionality to a devastating power!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489560/extras/lightning_laser_-_Kopie.gif?t=1731783948\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Complete <strong>over 300 challenges</strong> to gain the advantage of <strong>over 300 interesting unlocks</strong>, with <strong>quite a lot</strong> of new additions to the game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489560/extras/unlocks_gif.gif?t=1731783948\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose from over <strong>30 different events</strong> which may trigger throughout a run for even more variety and build customizing!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489560/extras/prophecy_options.gif?t=1731783948\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play through <strong>multiple realms</strong>, each one providing a different type of playstyle to all of the character classes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Craft</strong> your own weapon to take with you and overcome the <strong>5 trials</strong> of each realm!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Will you become the archmage of Elewar or will you be brought down by your opponents? Bulletheaven might quickly become a bullethell if you aren't strong enouph!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every enemy has at least 1 special attack... which you can dodge! There is no simple contact damage, which makes the game <strong>very challenging</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>Feature list:</strong></u></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">5 elements, 20 different offensive spells and 8 utility spells.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every spell may be upgraded in its rarity separately, which enables a diverse and powerful spell progression in a run.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Prophecy Whirls, which give you a choice of a random event, may challenge and reward you depending on the chosen difficulty.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">18 character classes with wildly different playstyles, combined with a dual class system. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">over 300 unlocks with corresponding rewards. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Over 140 upgrades.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose an unlocked blessing before you start a run, making cool combinations out of classes, blessings and starting spells possible!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">At least 5 realms with different enemies, rules and trials.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Crafting system to make your own items, which give you an additional edge in the Trials of Elewar. There are 5 different equipment slots with varying crafting.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Several hidden secrets to discover.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A roguelike gamemode with a highly different gameplay.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And much much more!</p></li></ul>","developers":["AL3xMK"],"dlc":[3202600],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489560/header.jpg?t=1731783948","is_free":true,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257045565,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257045565/movie480.mp4?t=1723670676","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257045565/movie_max.mp4?t=1723670676"},"name":"Release Trailer, Gameplay","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257045565/movie.293x165.jpg?t=1723670676","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257045565/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1723670676","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257045565/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1